\begin{center}
\vspace*{0.5cm}
{\Large\color{ScriptureGold}\ensuremath{\dagger}}

\vspace{0.3cm}

{\Large\bfseries\color{ChapterPurple} 詩歌默想}\\[0.1cm]
{\normalsize Hymn Meditation}

\vspace{0.5cm}

{\fontsize{20}{24}\selectfont\bfseries\color{SpiritBlue} Glorious Freedom}\\[0.2cm]
{\Large\color{ChapterPurple} 榮耀的釋放}

\vspace{0.3cm}

{\small\color{LightGray}\itshape
Words: Haldor Lillenas · Music: Alfred Judson (1917)}

\vspace{0.5cm}

\fcolorbox{ScriptureGold}{ScriptureBg!90}{%
\begin{minipage}{4.2in}
\vspace{0.3cm}
\centering
\itshape\color{ChapterPurple}
\small
Once I was bound by sin's galling fetters,\\
Chained like a slave I struggled in vain;\\
But I received a glorious freedom,\\
When Jesus broke my fetters in twain.\\[0.3em]

\textbf{Glorious freedom, wonderful freedom,}\\
\textbf{No more in chains of sin I repine!}\\
\textbf{Jesus the glorious Emancipator,}\\
\textbf{Now and forever He shall be mine.}
\vspace{0.3cm}
\end{minipage}
}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\fcolorbox{ChapterPurple}{white!95}{%
\begin{minipage}{4.2in}
\vspace{0.3cm}
\centering
\color{ChapterPurple}
\small
從前我被罪惡捆綁，\\
如囚犯掙扎徒然；\\
如今我得榮耀釋放，\\
主耶穌斷我鎖鏈。\\[0.3em]

\textbf{榮耀釋放，奇妙釋放！}\\
\textbf{罪惡鎖鏈已全斷開！}\\
\textbf{耶穌我主，榮耀救主！}\\
\textbf{永遠永遠屬於我！}
\vspace{0.3cm}
\end{minipage}
}

\vspace{0.3cm}

{\small\color{TextGray}
Freedom from all the carnal affections,\\
Freedom from envy, hatred and strife;\\
Freedom from vain and worldly ambitions,\\
Freedom from all that saddened my life.\\[0.2em]
\color{LightGray}\itshape
脫離一切肉體私情，脫離嫉恨與紛爭；\\
脫離虛空世上野心，脫離一切煩惱事。}

\vspace{0.4cm}

\fcolorbox{JesusRed}{white!95}{%
\begin{minipage}{4.2in}
\vspace{0.2cm}
\centering
\small\jesus{「你們必曉得真理，真理必叫你們得以自由。」}\\
\jesus{"You will know the truth, and the truth will set you free."}\\[0.1em]
\normalfont\color{LightGray}
— 約翰福音 John 8:32
\vspace{0.2cm}
\end{minipage}
}

\vspace{0.3cm}

{\footnotesize\color{LightGray}\itshape
這首詩歌完美詮釋了哥林多前書的核心信息：\\
在基督裏我們得著真正的自由——\\
不是放縱的自由，而是愛中的自由。}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\ornamentdiv

\end{center}
